{"tid":2133835,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"為甚麼是蓬佩奧？  資深傳媒人 - 潘小濤","createTime":"2020-07-31T10:25:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T10:58:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c46375ca00ead1b147a3ab80cb90575ce10805ff","tid":2133835,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T10:25:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200731/74JIA4X7GO3PX6N6JBMZ4UVGHU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200731%2F74JIA4X7GO3PX6N6JBMZ4UVGHU%2F&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG1zUVmWcutTvqHtF1LT7nQkc%3D&h=2321da0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200731%2F74JIA4X7GO3PX6N6JBMZ4UVGHU%2F&h=ed0503d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200731/74JIA4X7GO3PX6N6JBMZ4UVGHU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n為甚麼是蓬佩奧？ <br />\n資深傳媒人 - 潘小濤<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/32QUu0_iCpFW3W2KpnWph0JhVX4=/1997x1000/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/A2QXZEIU5JO77SKAI6NANF6HWE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F32QUu0_iCpFW3W2KpnWph0JhVX4%3D%2F1997x1000%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FA2QXZEIU5JO77SKAI6NANF6HWE.jpg&h=248f4ee0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日美國國務卿蓬佩奧人氣很盛，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n當年列根去到西德控制的西柏林，與。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n上周四蓬佩奧的演講題目為〈共產中國與自由世界的未來〉，也是精心計算的。美。。。。。。。。。。。勞。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧說：「如果我們現在屈膝，我們的子孫後代可能會受中國共。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對華強硬絕非選舉策略<br />\n<br />\n習近平上台後放棄韜光養晦，不斷要另立擺脫歐美的國際新秩序&mdash;&mdash;滲透聯合國等國際組織、推出一帶一路、大張旗鼓在南海造島、。。。。。。。。。<br />\n溫。<br />\n<br />\n值得注意的是，如此重大政策宣示，竟非特朗普親自宣佈，而是由國務卿昭告天下，這應該不是侵侵想留有餘地，與北京維持一定的政策迴旋空間，而是侵侵的國際形象不討好，難以吸引國際社會興趣，遑論團結各國結盟抗共了。相反，蓬佩奧這位西點軍校高材生（工程管理學第一名），冷戰時期是負責巡邏西德與東德和捷克斯洛伐克邊境的美國陸軍軍官，曾任國會議員，也是前任的中情局局長。這樣的背景，發表這種拒共演講，應有足夠說服力了。<br />\n<br />\n更重要的是，這是明確的告訴中共，對華政策的重大轉變絕非選舉策略，而是會付諸行動。就在蓬佩奧宣告結束與中國「盲目交往」同一周，美國就指控侯斯頓的中國總領事館涉及間諜行為，下令其關閉。這是用來附和蓬佩奧的，證明他是動真格的，不像以前的總統那樣僅停留於口頭警告。<br />\n<br />\n這是埋葬過去50年中美關係的演講，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n潘小濤<br />\n資深傳媒人"},{"pid":"9791f22723cfb97e8fd80a1b57a5baf6b87a469f","tid":2133835,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T10:31:28.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad7930555f278880c67219564ac77b284b34f8d","tid":2133835,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T10:34:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c564c94a55e6e2f33b387f636f85ee786a3be3c6","tid":2133835,"uid":117225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T10:36:04.000Z","msg":"因為區區共匪唔值得美國總統應對"},{"pid":"f71e03be6ffebb585155aef857af34b0aeea5a38","tid":2133835,"uid":7057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T10:51:16.000Z","msg":"可惜佢可能只可以做多半年"},{"pid":"ac0005368db6619d69a8585372fe21213f631953","tid":2133835,"uid":185424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T10:55:35.000Z","msg":"希望佢會4年後選總統"},{"pid":"f88398a47be298487479a22cc6461757164f3028","tid":2133835,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f71e03be6ffebb585155aef857af34b0aeea5a38","tid":2133835,"uid":7057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T10:51:16.000Z","msg":"可惜佢可能只可以做多半年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T10:58:04.000Z","msg":"關你撚事呀吊你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 選總統又話你知呀"},{"pid":"26463dc645d91fcd076417d8d1c04a9fd54db658","tid":2133835,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f88398a47be29848